<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Ella Rae Wise almost comes to blows with Chloe Meadows and Courtney Green on Sunday's episode of TOWIE.</p>

<p>Tensions simmer as Ella and Clelia Theodorou have an argument with Chloe and Courtney about Chloe Brockett having a fling with Ella's ex Jack McDermott. </p>

<p>Ella was furious over Chloe Brockett's actions and took her anger out on Chloe Meadows and Courtney, unhappy that they were defending her. </p>

<p>Tension: Ella Rae Wise almost comes to blows with Chloe Meadows and Courtney Green on Sunday's episode of TOWIE</p>

<p>In scenes set to air on the next episode, Courtney and Chloe Meadows were relaxing in a park when they were approached by Ella and Clelia.</p>

<p>Sensing a confrontation was about to happen, Courtney said: 'So what's going on?'</p>

<p>Ella replied: 'I think you know, don't you?'</p>

<p>Courtney came to Chloe Brockett's defense and said: 'I know what you've been saying about stuff with Chloe, and she has admitted it. What I want you to know is that she didn't actually do it out of spite.'</p>

<p>Argument: Tensions simmer as Ella and Clelia Theodorou have an argument with Chloe and Courtney about Chloe Brockett having a fling with Ella's ex Jack McDermott.</p>

<p>Unimpressed, Ella said: 'To me, you don't do it. I don't condone stuff like that.'</p>

<p>Chloe Meadows then chimed in and said to Ella: 'At the end of the day, you two have not been friends for a long time. She doesn't have any loyalties to you.'</p>

<p>Getting angrier by the minute, Ella shot back: 'I'm not being funny, you can sit there and defend her as much as you want because you are her mates, I get it. But if the shoe was on the other foot, how would you actually feel?'</p>

<p>Before either of the girls had a chance to respond, Clelia jumped in and said: 'I just think it looks so bad guys. She shouldn't have done that. </p>

<p>Confrontation: Ella was furious over Chloe Brockett's actions and took her anger out on Chloe Meadows and Courtney, unhappy that they were defending her</p>

<p>Chloe Meadows said to Ella: 'At the end of the day, you two have not been friends for a long time. She doesn't have any loyalties to you' </p>

<p>'Imagine you guys had fallen out and then Courtney goes and does that to you. It's so wrong girls, it is so wrong.'    </p>

<p>Whether or not Ella and Chloe Brockett will manage to patch things up after their fallout remains to be seen. </p>

<p>The 10th anniversary series was due to start filming in March 2020, but ITV bosses made the tough decision to put the production on pause due to the coronavirus pandemic. </p>

<p>Fans were left without their Essex fix until the show came back with a vengeance on Sunday night, with former cast member Amy Childs returning.</p>

<p>Ella shot back: 'If the shoe was on the other foot, how would you actually feel?'</p>

<p>There will also be surprise appearances from some of the show's other big stars from the past decade.</p>

<p>Paul Mortimer, Head of Digital Channels and Acquisitions for ITV, added: 'After 10 years, TOWIE is still going strong and remains the number one show on ITVBe.</p>

<p>'We're thrilled to be welcoming back new and old faces for the upcoming mega-series as the show celebrates this special anniversary.'</p>

<p>The Only Way Is Essex airs on Sunday on ITVBe at 9pm. </p>

